{"tid":745893,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食評：圓方pizza deco pizzeria","createTime":"2018-07-17T06:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T12:13:18.000Z","uid":181719,"like":10,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e12352e19c2a8f2ec0da00e47594db41bbbb5a97","tid":745893,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:55:12.000Z","msg":"放假去行吓呢個貴一貴嘅商場，發現呢間餐廳，188就有個3層架tea set，包 2 杯野飲添，喺呢個場算好很平啦，就入去試吓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/144016_d9e93689f1f4ba76e443dd89bee963ac.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F144016_d9e93689f1f4ba76e443dd89bee963ac.jpeg&h=96084c6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/144025_b4cc28bbf3fc400703120928e1adc8ea.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F144025_b4cc28bbf3fc400703120928e1adc8ea.jpeg&h=787cb371&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n難得星期日下晝，客人都係好疏落，所以都好快有野食。由最底果層開始講，呢個和牛海蝦薄餅，係要另加30蚊嘅，但係加咗之後完全唔後悔，因為澳州和牛肉味濃得黎又唔韌，海蝦咬感亦相當彈牙，係個好好食嘅批黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果唔加錢，可以揀啲普通嘅款式，例如夏威夷風光果啲。有波羅有辣肉腸咁。食呢種批好似會得罪意大利人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/144033_fe770bd395545f63e1a32d7304848e46.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F144033_fe770bd395545f63e1a32d7304848e46.jpeg&h=44275bc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/144040_f8e512262e33f194ab20193e4671c131.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F144040_f8e512262e33f194ab20193e4671c131.jpeg&h=11d8de14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二層就好三妻四妾喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有炸雞啦炸魷魚啦parma ham啦辣肉腸啦牛油果蟹肉多士啦，仲有啲橙皮添！（其實係檸檬黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）。炸雞、辣肉腸同parma ham係正常味道，唔特別講。炸魷魚炸粉薄，口感爽，食第一舊點沙律醬已經幾好食，第二舊（每人唔只一舊都好抵讚）點黑色果隻甜酸汁，直頭係好好食喎。不過最特別都係個牛油果蟹肉多士，特別在我唔中意食牛油果，都覺得佢好好食，而且佢嘅蟹肉係一舊舊唔係一絲絲的，飽滿、豐富 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/144049_5a9a8f9423069d2215fc40bd8d9df130.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F144049_5a9a8f9423069d2215fc40bd8d9df130.jpeg&h=d327619b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/144054_7333684dbdfe378370e49d9809e91dd2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F144054_7333684dbdfe378370e49d9809e91dd2.jpeg&h=4d4d285c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最頂果層嘅朱古力蛋糕同芒果撻，有一個好精準嘅形容，就係大學canteen糕點嘅級數，好食過餅咭小小啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係總括黎講188（+30）加一，我覺得係好抵食嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/144104_b670959db2a19154d1c156e7e763e209.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F144104_b670959db2a19154d1c156e7e763e209.jpeg&h=0fc12db1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後講返個批，唔加錢嘅選擇除咗夏威夷風光之外，仲有個港式叉燒，我覺得好特別嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下次會再去試。"},{"pid":"3b660b5913038161bebb271e5b457f0e3d3e9fff","tid":745893,"uid":39215,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:57:36.000Z","msg":"幾錢一個post？"},{"pid":"2c4c41525a744910c4a41a3075c732e61529e688","tid":745893,"uid":57488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:58:45.000Z","msg":"港式叉燒pizza<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6b746b0cca6341657cde66ae923311fb6552949","tid":745893,"uid":174846,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T07:16:02.000Z","msg":"星期日都冇客要搵打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c1cb7001e2ca7edd4089f768b535ce7b24cbb95","tid":745893,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2c4c41525a744910c4a41a3075c732e61529e688","tid":745893,"uid":57488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:58:45.000Z","msg":"港式叉燒pizza<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T07:42:17.000Z","msg":"未食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但聽落幾特別丫"},{"pid":"cbbc4a79a3379407961f39c758eadbe442309382","tid":745893,"uid":154684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T07:44:59.000Z","msg":"抵食喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1bfc7ca836f7ef26e303b99f92d8896d6a57bad","tid":745893,"uid":39948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:14:51.000Z","msg":"有AE咭先會去"},{"pid":"ae9536c46b15d39b4ee130c3c436b750d427841e","tid":745893,"uid":181719,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"cbbc4a79a3379407961f39c758eadbe442309382","tid":745893,"uid":154684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T07:44:59.000Z","msg":"抵食喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:27:24.000Z","msg":"係呀，呢個場、呢個價位、比呢啲野食<br />\n我都預咗又比人話係打手<br />\n但除咗啲甜品唔得，其實冇咩可以彈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b49417f114b12afbc48a5f8e2bacd252b25fd5","tid":745893,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1bfc7ca836f7ef26e303b99f92d8896d6a57bad","tid":745893,"uid":39948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":